---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Social Proof for Jewelers — Build Trust & Drive Sales | SocialProof" description="Showcase customer testimonials and reviews on your jewelry store website. SocialProof helps jewelers convert browsers into buyers with authentic social proof. Free." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/for/jewelers">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #555; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; padding: .9rem 2.25rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; }
    .trust-bar { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 2rem; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; background: #f8fafc; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #555; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    section { max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .benefits-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .benefit-card { background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .benefit-card .icon { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .benefit-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .5rem; }
    .benefit-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #555; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5; }
    .quote-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .quote-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .quote-text { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 1rem; font-style: italic; }
    .quote-author { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; }
    .quote-role { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #888; }
    .stars { color: #f59e0b; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
    .steps { counter-reset: step; }
    .step { display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; align-items: flex-start; }
    .step-num { background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; width: 2rem; height: 2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.9rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: .15rem; }
    .step h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .35rem; }
    .step p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #555; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5; }
    .cta-block { text-align: center; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3rem 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; }
    .cta-block h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .cta-block p { color: #bfdbfe; max-width: 440px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .cta-block .cta-btn { background: #fff; color: #2563eb; }
    footer { border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; color: #999; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .benefits-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/for/">Industries</a>
    <a href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-nav">Try free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <h1>Social proof for jewelers — turn browsers into confident buyers</h1>
  <p>Jewelry purchases are deeply personal and high-consideration. Real customer testimonials on your website build the trust that turns interest into a sale. Free to start.</p>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-btn">Start free today →</a>
</div>

<div class="trust-bar">
  <span>💎 Built for independent jewelers</span>
  <span>✓ Works on Shopify, Squarespace & more</span>
  <span>✓ Custom branding</span>
  <span>✓ 5-minute setup</span>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>Why jewelers need testimonials on their website</h2>
  <div class="benefits-grid">
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="icon">💍</div>
      <h3>High-stakes purchases need reassurance</h3>
      <p>Engagement rings, anniversary gifts, custom pieces — these are once-in-a-lifetime purchases. Customers need to feel completely confident before spending hundreds or thousands. Real testimonials provide that reassurance.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="icon">🛒</div>
      <h3>Compete with the big retailers</h3>
      <p>Kay, Zales, and Tiffany have name recognition. Independent jewelers win on craftsmanship, personalization, and customer experience — and testimonials are how you prove that to strangers online.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="icon">✨</div>
      <h3>Custom work deserves to be shown off</h3>
      <p>If you do custom designs, engraving, or repairs, client stories are your portfolio. "They recreated my grandmother's ring perfectly" is more powerful than any product photo.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="icon">📱</div>
      <h3>Capture mobile shoppers researching online</h3>
      <p>Most jewelry research happens on phones. A testimonial widget that loads fast and looks beautiful on mobile turns casual browsers into in-store or online buyers.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="background:#f8fafc; margin:0; padding: 3rem 2rem; max-width:100%;">
  <div style="max-width:880px; margin:0 auto;">
    <h2>What your widget could look like</h2>
    <div class="quote-grid">
      <div class="quote-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="quote-text">"I brought in my grandmother's old brooch and they transformed it into a modern pendant that she would have loved. The attention to detail was extraordinary. I'll never go anywhere else."</p>
        <div class="quote-author">Rebecca S.</div>
        <div class="quote-role">Custom jewelry client</div>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="quote-text">"They helped me design the perfect engagement ring on my budget without making me feel rushed or embarrassed. She said yes and couldn't stop showing people the ring. Worth every penny."</p>
        <div class="quote-author">Marcus W.</div>
        <div class="quote-role">Engagement ring customer</div>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-card">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="quote-text">"Went in for a simple ring sizing and left with a necklace I didn't know I needed. The staff is so knowledgeable and genuinely excited about their pieces. Real gem of a shop."</p>
        <div class="quote-author">Diana L.</div>
        <div class="quote-role">Repeat customer</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Getting started takes 5 minutes</h2>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Create your free account</h3>
        <p>Sign up with your email. No credit card required. Your free account includes one beautiful testimonial widget, forever.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Collect testimonials from happy customers</h3>
        <p>Share your unique collection link via email, text, or on your receipt. Customers fill out a simple form — name, optional photo, and a few sentences about their purchase.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Curate what appears on your site</h3>
        <p>You approve every testimonial before it goes live. Keep your widget polished with the stories that best represent your work and service.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">4</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Embed on your website or online store</h3>
        <p>Paste one line of code into your website. Works with Shopify, Squarespace, Wix, WordPress, or any custom site.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="cta-block">
    <h2>Show the world why customers love your jewelry</h2>
    <p>Free forever for 1 widget. Start collecting testimonials in minutes.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-btn">Create your free account →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2025 SocialProof · <a href="/for/" style="color:#999">All industries</a> · <a href="/pricing" style="color:#999">Pricing</a> · <a href="/privacy" style="color:#999">Privacy</a></p>
</footer>

<div class="footer-links" style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:0.9rem;">
  <strong style="color:#374151;">Also explore:</strong>
  <a href="/for/coaches" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Coaches</a>
  <a href="/for/freelancers" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Freelancers</a>
  <a href="/for/restaurants" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Restaurants</a>
  <a href="/vs/senja" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Senja</a>
  <a href="/vs/testimonial" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Testimonial.to</a>
</div>
</Base>
